00:59:12,030 --> 00:59:14,950
I want you to collect
$200 from each of 'em.

847
00:59:16,380 --> 00:59:18,260
- [Tommy On Tape] I'll double it.

848
00:59:18,260 --> 00:59:21,110
- [Harris On Tape] Well, that
