01:19:35,733 --> 01:19:37,420
- And what if there's a leak in the FBI?

1144
01:19:37,420 --> 01:19:40,760
All right, I'm hiding out here in town.

1145
01:19:40,760 --> 01:19:42,024
- I want you safe.

1146
